text: Teltscher is a surname of German origin and means inhibitant of Teltsch (town in the Czech Republic). People with that name include: * Eliot Teltscher (born 1959), retired professional American tennis player * Josef Eduard Teltscher (born 1801), Austrian painter and lithographer * Mark Teltscher (active from 2005), English poker player ==See also== * Category:Surnames of German origin
title: Teltscher
